Guys, keep coming back here.

00:03:10.630 --> 00:03:14.260
I'm gonna keep bringing tips like this for
training...we're gonna get you some of the

00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:18.340
nutrition tips you've been asking for and
a whole lot other stuff that you may not have

00:03:18.340 --> 00:03:19.340
thought about.

